{"tid":2151372,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"［本地音樂節］約你睇個show TONE MUSIC FESTIVAL","createTime":"2020-08-11T10:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T15:48:22.000Z","uid":144079,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e94a95dfb0d6f8202b0034dc71e6af18962ac733","tid":2151372,"uid":144079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:57:22.000Z","msg":"枉連登成日講本土、黃圈，成個連登居然一個post都無。<br />\n<br />\nTONE ONLINE MUSIC FESTIVAL 5月已經搞過一次，5個鐘嘅節目免費俾你慢慢睇。<br />\n嚟緊10月再添食無它，都係想班台前幕後兄弟有工開、搵兩餐飯食。<br />\n<br />\n今次有11組表演者，一樣係全土炮音樂人，有仔有女、有老有嫩，重有一組啱你口味。<br />\nInstinct of Sight<br />\niii iris liu<br />\nJason Kui<br />\nkz (Dehumanization Association)<br />\nManiac<br />\nPanther Chan 陳蕾<br />\nSilHungMo 小紅帽<br />\nSmoke in Half Note<br />\nTyson Yoshi<br />\nWhite Dimension<br />\n乙女シンドリーム - 乙女新夢<br />\n<br />\n本身睇直播就免費嘅，不過我哋想實質支持就一樣可以買飛課金。<br />\n買咗飛重可以錄影當日去現場睇，同有一堆merch送，又本地啤、又啤牌、又嘢食咁，真係丁屎咁細張飛，包到成個降落傘咁大。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋要募夠500,000 先夠打個和，重要500,000係只計成本，個幾個搞手變相做幾個月義工。<br />\n真係搞手只求打個和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家賣咗成個月先募得個七萬，照咁落去個幾個搞手好大幾會入曬肉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dex4oeM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDex4oeM.jpg&h=200226c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地成日講黃色經濟圈，但係除咗食飯幫襯黃店、買下蘋果日報、買埋282之外你重做過啲咩？個圈會唔會太細？<br />\n呢班人，由舊年6月到宜家一路光合作用緊，我哋係咪應該行多步幫下佢哋，更重要嘅係發展下香港本地音樂文化。<br />\n可能你會話啲bands聽都未聽過去，肯定係啲二打六嚟，不過你要知到無嘢係突然石頭爆出嚟，我哋唔幫，佢哋點爭扎都唔會突破到。<br />\n<br />\n最後香港人，幫香港人！10月31日，約定你！<br />\nPS.呢班人黃到閪咁<br />\n<br />\n官方facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/Thistownneeds/photos/a.138804342845932/3348852271841107/?type=3&amp;sfnsn=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FThistownneeds%2Fphotos%2Fa.138804342845932%2F3348852271841107%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26sfnsn%3Dmo&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FhVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=2aa9d657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/Thistownneeds/photos/a.138804342845932/3348852271841107/?type=3&amp;sfnsn=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n購票網站<br />\n<a href=\"https://tickcats.co/ticket/tone2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftickcats.co%2Fticket%2Ftone2%2F&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FhVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=4d47dea8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tickcats.co/ticket/tone2/</a><br />\n<br />\n第一次個live<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yvMl8v8PRVE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyvMl8v8PRVE&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FhVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=4e001bd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yvMl8v8PRVE</a>"},{"pid":"fe510336b0bb189c3c9a40f9c1692fb8fa71a4f8","tid":2151372,"uid":144079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:58:27.000Z","msg":"終於開啱台<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd83490a532eea71f87ca7551fd0e52023c5ff98","tid":2151372,"uid":144079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:27:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"173f0294ce0cbe9c0fc08fb89789ec79d189571f","tid":2151372,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:27:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a80e335986e7fb64f0ca202134542c419ffa48","tid":2151372,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:28:09.000Z","msg":"黃色音樂圈"},{"pid":"bfa56580ed4868d69a724600f30c8a3ad97d8668","tid":2151372,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:28:48.000Z","msg":"其實本土音樂好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1089a383169540702bc677cf7de224920d6ee74e","tid":2151372,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:29:16.000Z","msg":"其實本土音樂好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"465919a3c4f4b711b942cbd13020b3cfdad9a602","tid":2151372,"uid":22254